# Source media not used on the site. Only the single-digit numbered images
# (1.jpg, 2.png, ...) in each project folder are referenced in the code;
# the raw photos, screen recordings, and .mp4 demo files are kept locally
# but excluded from git (some are >100MB and GitHub rejects them).
/public/imgs/*/*
!/public/imgs/*/[0-9].*
# The "Beyond Code" gallery uses every image in its folder, so track them all.
!/public/imgs/Beyond Code/*

# Local-only backup of original (uncompressed) images.
/public/imgs_original/
